加里·鲍威尔确认了 Libertines 新专辑的发行日期https://www.nme.com/news/music/gary-powell-confirms-release-date-for-new-libertines-album-3495496?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=gary-powell-confirms-release-date-为新浪荡子专辑Damian JonesSat, 09 Sep 2023 10:23:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3495496 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="浪荡子加里·鲍威尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自 2019 年以来，乐队一直在制作《Anthems For Doomed Youth》的后续作品</p><p>加里<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gary-powell-confirms-release-date-for-new-libertines-album-3495496">·鲍威尔 (Gary Powell) 确认 Libertines 新专辑发行日期的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="浪荡子加里·鲍威尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/the-libertines-gary-powell-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">Libertines</a>鼓手加里·鲍威尔 (Gary Powell) 已确认乐队即将发行的新专辑何时发行。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-libertines-interview-up-the-bracket-album-20-years-pete-doherty-carl-barat-jamie-t-3359042">我们从与 The Libertines 的对话视频聊天中了解到的五件事</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://oliverspencer.co.uk/blogs/journal/four-on-the-floor-episode-1-gary-powell" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>奥利弗·斯宾塞 (Oliver Spencer)</em></a>的最新采访中，这位坚持者更新了乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-libertines-new-album-anthems-for-doomed-youth-track-by-track-first-listen-review-16186">2015 年 LP 专辑《Anthems For Doomed Youth》</a>的后续版本何时上市。</p><p>他说：“我们刚刚录制了最新专辑。我想我们每十年左右就会做一次。是的。所以期待下一个来自坟墓！该专辑将于 [2024] 一月发行。”</p><p>该乐队自 2019 年以来一直在制作新唱片， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-have-just-returned-from-working-on-their-new-album-in-jamaica-3319911">去年在牙买加制作了这张唱片</a>。</p><p>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carl-barat">卡尔·巴拉特 (Carl Barât)</a>在<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/in-conversation"><em>In Conversation</em></a>系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-give-update-on-new-album-with-different-energy-3361680">节目中</a>说道：“从声音上来说，我们想做一些以前从未做过的事情……我认为我们会寻求以与以前不同的能量来做一些事情。但我们还没有到那个阶段。” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_thelibertines_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">浪荡子乐队的卡尔·巴拉特和加里·鲍威尔 图片来源：Medios y Media/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>乐队还分享了一首名为《Shiver》的新歌的细节， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">Pete Doherty</a>解释说，这首歌曲“真正感性地让人回想起”之前 Libertines 剪辑的《The Delaney》、《France》和《Music When The Lights Go Out》。联合主唱巴拉特表示同意，并补充道：“是的，‘颤抖’很棒。事实上，我昨晚就在听。”</p><p>鲍威尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-gary-powell-new-album-steam-packet-uk-tour-label-interview-3287083">此前还告诉<em>NME</em></a> ，他的重点是乐队第四张专辑的“前进”。 “好处是每个人都在写作，”他说。 “显然，我们不会尝试重新发明轮子……但我认为我们可以把船推得更远一点，同时仍然带来观众在观看浪荡子表演时所渴望的同样情感完整性和活力的东西”。</p><p> Doherty 表示，当他们在 2019 年首次开始录制这张唱片时，乐队一直在探索新材料的许多雄心勃勃的方向，将其比作<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-clash">The Clash</a>分裂的“Sandinista”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/freestyle-rap-sandinista-pete-doherty-tells-us-whats-going-on-with-the-libertines-new-album-2482089">多样性</a>。</p><p> “卡尔想要用我们拥有的所有这些疯狂的想法来做一件‘桑地诺’的事情，所以我们将拥有所有这些自由风格的东西和民谣的东西，然后还有更传统的多尔蒂/巴拉特歌曲，”多尔蒂当时说。 “我不认为加里和约翰的歌曲是其中的一部分，因为它们是非常非常有力的歌曲。”</p><p>前<em>NME</em>记者马特·威尔金森 (Matt Wilkinson) 在回顾他们的上一张专辑时将<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-libertines-new-album-anthems-for-doomed-youth-track-by-track-first-listen-review-16186">这张唱片描述为“The Libertines 制作过的最全面的专辑”</a> 。</p><p>与此同时，一部关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-documentary-about-pete-doherty-to-premiere-at-zurich-film-festival-3490436">皮特·多尔蒂的新纪录片将于本月晚些时候在苏黎世电影节上首映</a>。</p><p>加里<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gary-powell-confirms-release-date-for-new-libertines-album-3495496">·鲍威尔 (Gary Powell) 确认 Libertines 新专辑发行日期的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
