etty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fall-out-boy-metro-boomin-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fall-out-boy-metro-boomin-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fall-out-boy-metro-boomin-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/fall-out-boy-metro-boomin-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fall-out-boy">Fall Out Boy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metro-boomin">Metro Boomin</a>已被添加到下周 2023 年 MTV 音乐录影带大奖的表演者名单中。</p><p>颁奖典礼将于 9 月 12 日在新泽西州纽瓦克的保德信中心举行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-to-perform-at-2023-mtv-vmas-3495027">最近宣布的奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>也将出席颁奖典礼。</p><p>其他将在 2023 年 VMA 上表演的乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maneskin">Måneskin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>等，以及新宣布的 Peso Pluma。这将是 Fall Out Boy 自 2007 年以来首次在该剧中表演。</p><p>上个月公布的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-sza-and-doja-cat-lead-mtv-vmas-2023-nominations-3480130">提名名单中</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a> 、Doja Cat 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>领衔。</p><p>斯威夫特以八项提名遥遥领先，SZA 获得六项提名，Doja Cat、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-petras">Kim Petras</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-smith">Sam Smith</a>各获得五项提名。整个艺术家团队也都在角逐今年的年​​度视频类别。 </p><figure id="attachment_2698328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2698328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2698328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/GettyImages-1170428323.jpg" alt="MTV 音乐录影带大奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://