p-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweekendv2_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweekendv2_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweekendv2_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweekendv2_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>录音学院裁定，人工智能生成的模仿<a href="/artists/drake">德雷克</a>和<a href="/artists/the-weeknd">威肯的</a>声音的合作将没有资格获得格莱美奖。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ai-music-oasis-liam-gallagher-drake-weeknd-3432529">在人工智能绿洲时代，平凡是没有意义的</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/05/arts/music/ghostwriter-whiplash-travis-scott-21-savage.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>报道，本周早些时候，由匿名制作人 Ghostwriter 创作和制作的歌曲《Heart On My Sleeve》已提交格莱美评选，分为最佳说唱歌曲和歌曲两个类别。年度最佳——这两个奖项都授予歌曲作者，而不是表演者。</p><p>据信，唱片学院首席执行官小哈维·梅森也表示，这首歌可能符合创意，并且是人类创作和录制的原创作品。正因为如此，梅森补充道：“它绝对符合条件，因为它是由人类编写的。”</p><p>但提交的要求之一是，该曲目必须“通过实体店、第三方在线零售商和/或流媒体服务在全国范围内销售”，这可能会成为绊脚石，因为它<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-music-strip-viral-ai-generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-collaboration-from-streaming-platforms-3432055">被环球音乐</a>禁止<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-music-strip-viral-ai-generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-collaboration-from-streaming-platforms-3432055">该组织于今年早些时候首次出现后不久</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cw6xctbOH79/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-